cnt2RegistrationNum.name: cnt2RegistrationNum
cnt2RegistrationNum.description: The number of registerations received from subagents.

cnt2RegistrationTable.name: cnt2RegistrationTable
cnt2RegistrationTable.description: A list of registration entries. The number of registrations is given by the value of cnt2RegstrationNum.

cnt2RegistrationEntry.name: cnt2RegistrationEntry
cnt2RegistrationEntry.description: A subagent entry containing objects known about the subagents by the master agent.

cnt2RegisterIndex.name: cnt2RegisterIndex
cnt2RegisterIndex.description: A unique value for each registration. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of cnt2RegistrationNum. The order in which entries exist in this table identifies the chronological order in which subagent registrations occurred.

cnt2RegisterSlot.name: cnt2RegisterSlot
cnt2RegisterSlot.description: The slot number for this subagent if it is connected over the switch. If it is TCP or UDP connected, this value is 0.

cnt2RegisterProtocol.name: cnt2RegisterProtocol
cnt2RegisterProtocol.description: The protocol used to interface to this subagent.

cnt2RegisterTransport.name: cnt2RegisterTransport
cnt2RegisterTransport.description: The transport method/protocol underlying the master/subagent protocol that is used to interface to this subagent.

cnt2RegisterAgentDescr.name: cnt2RegisterAgentDescr
cnt2RegisterAgentDescr.description: A textual string containing a description of the registering subagent.

cnt2RegisterGroup.name: cnt2RegisterGroup
cnt2RegisterGroup.description: The group object identifier used by the subagent to register. If the subagent registered a row, this will reflect the table identifier.

cnt2RegisterMibVersion.name: cnt2RegisterMibVersion
cnt2RegisterMibVersion.description: A textual string containing a reference to the body administering the registered tree and the version of the registered tree. The string will be in one of the following forms: RFC xxxx - xxxx is the RFC number, CNT x.y - x is the major version, y is the minor version, IETF vv/mmm/yy - (IETF Draft), vv is the version, mmm is a three character month code, yy is the year, NAME vv/mmm/yy - NAME is a Standards Body name, vv is the version, mmm is a three character month code, yy is the year.

cnt2RegisterUpTime.name: cnt2RegisterUpTime
cnt2RegisterUpTime.description: The time that the subagent has been registered, relative to the master agent.

cnt2RegisterRowInstance.name: cnt2RegisterRowInstance
cnt2RegisterRowInstance.description: A textual string containing the following format: *.x1[.x2.x3...xn], where * - the OID range registered by the subagent, xn - object idenifier representing instance OIDs registered by the subagent. when appended to cnt2RegisterGroup, the entire OID is the group and row registered by the subagent.
